<i>noun</i>: 홍보 [홍보], 판촉 [판촉], 추진 [추진], 진흥 [진ː흥], 진급 [진ː급], 조성 [조ː성], 전도 [전도], 육성 [육썽], 영전 [영전], 승진 [승진], 승급 [승급], 선양 [서냥], 격상 [격쌍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>홍보 [홍보]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; publicity; advertisement</dd><br>
<dd>널리 알림. 또는 그 소식.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of promoting a product, service, program, etc., widely to a certain target; or such a promotion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>판촉 [판촉]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 방법을 써서 소비자의 구매욕을 자극하여 판매가 늘도록 유도하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of boosting sales by stimulating a customer's desire to purchase something through many different methods.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>추진 [추진]</dt><br>
<dd>1. propulsion; pushing; driving</dd><br>
<dd>물체를 밀어 앞으로 나아가게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of pushing an object and making it move forward.</dd><br>
<dd>2. pushing ahead; promotion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 목적을 위해서 일을 밀고 나아감.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of proceeding with a project for a certain purpose.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진흥 [진ː흥]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 널리 알려 기운이나 세력을 활발하게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making something known or propagating it widely to make it become active or influential.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진급 [진ː급]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; advancement</dd><br>
<dd>계급, 등급, 학년 등이 올라감.</dd><br>
<dd>Advancement in one's rank, class, grade, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조성 [조ː성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. building; development</dd><br>
<dd>무엇을 만들어서 이룸.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making and establishing something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fostering; promotion; instigation</dd><br>
<dd>분위기나 흐름 등을 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of creating an atmosphere or trend.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전도 [전도]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; propagation</dd><br>
<dd>종교에서, 교리를 세상에 널리 알려 사람들에게 종교를 믿게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>In religion, the act of widely spreading doctrines and causing people to believe in one's religion.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>육성 [육썽]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; fostering</dd><br>
<dd>인력이나 산업, 문화 등을 보살펴서 성장하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of nurturing and growing human resources, industry, culture, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>영전 [영전]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion</dd><br>
<dd>공공 기관이나 회사 등에서 전보다 더 좋은 자리나 직위로 옮김.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being moved to a better position or higher title in a public organization, company, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>승진 [승진]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; advancement</dd><br>
<dd>직장에서 지금보다 더 높은 자리에 오름.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moving up to a higher position at one's workplace.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>승급 [승급]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; advancement</dd><br>
<dd>급수나 등급, 직위 등이 오름.</dd><br>
<dd>Advancement in one's level, rank, position, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>선양 [서냥]</dt><br>
<dd>exaltation; promotion</dd><br>
<dd>권위나 명성 등을 널리 알려지게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of widely spreading the reputation, prestige, etc., of something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>격상 [격쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>promotion; elevation</dd><br>
<dd>자격이나 등급, 지위 등이 높아짐. 또는 그것을 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>A rise in rank, position, or qualifications, or raising them.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>